</div><div class="indent"><strong>Hawk</strong>: My aching back, George! <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DefiedTrope" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DefiedTrope">Forget that going down with the ship stuff!</a>
